{"tid":1429882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以救吓我老母","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:17:52.000Z","uid":186387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d944598afb878c65b7860268f0c38fb4091dfbfd","tid":1429882,"uid":186387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"頭先唔小心同老母對話中提到鐳射筆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 啲人話用啲鐳射筆去觀星喎 佢地自己白痴都唔好當人白痴啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(心諗): 其實你咪就係嗰個白痴囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 吓 有咩問題 不嬲都係咁觀星㗎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 嗰啲筆呀 會射盲人對眼㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咁啲警察盲咗未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 佢地嗰啲筆呀 唔係你文具鋪買嗰啲呀 佢地嗰啲係美國佬俾錢買俾佢地嘅武器嚟！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: (聽到尼度放棄咗再同佢爭論)<br />\n<br />\n其實我真係好愛我老母 平常同佢關係都好好 但一講到尼啲事就會嘈交 (佢一地都堅持話自己係中立 然後只選擇接收反對示威者嗰一邊嘅資訊) 每次一嘈我都好想喊 嘈完個心就頂住頂住 我真係好想我老母可以睇清個事實 我唔想佢成為我心目中最卑視嗰班人 到底有咩方法可以幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11968b24238639ebaa74ed6d819db6657f75b9a9","tid":1429882,"uid":247639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d944598afb878c65b7860268f0c38fb4091dfbfd","tid":1429882,"uid":186387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"頭先唔小心同老母對話中提到鐳射筆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class